{"tid":1568877,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"港歌力量，無限共鳴 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-09-14T12:05:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T12:05:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0984e0433834b0bb524dc46e5db642680637312f","tid":1568877,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:05:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190914/20767778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190914%2F20767778&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSt%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=f6d07ff7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190914%2F20767778&h=67f46775\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190914/20767778</a><br />\n<br />\n港歌力量，無限共鳴 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190914/large/1568355830_4300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190914%2Flarge%2F1568355830_4300.jpg&h=2552f615&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n911恐襲事件18周年這天，香港全面停止所有抗爭活動，為恐襲喪生者受害者致哀，也不要落共方及傀儡政府「恐怖主義苗頭」口實，他們擅於羅織罪名插贓嫁禍毀屍滅跡──所以是日「文攻」大合唱。<br />\n<br />\n全港多區都出現X千人聚集合唱《願榮光歸香港》港歌，它才正式面世一天，已有逾百萬點擊和分享，而且很快大家都琅琅上口慷慨高歌，且有多國語言版本，多款剪輯MV版本，正如創作人之言：「音樂是凝聚人心最強武器」。<br />\n<br />\n溫柔的殺傷力一定令共方恐懼忌諱，不但遍地開花還全球滾動，逆權運動無畏無懼不屈不撓進行百日，港歌和人鏈一樣令人震撼──萬一某日霸權封殺鎮壓，它只會更紅，更強壯，更凝聚人心，文化、藝術、民意三結合，就是力量，無限共鳴。<br />\n<br />\n這種力量，豈是一儍戇紋身軍裝，自己玩警棍拍短片希望大展「雄風」可比？其同事反勸喻千萬不要再傳，「有責任保障警隊的聲譽」云云。<br />\n<br />\n至於數百收錢曾唱國歌及紅歌的鄉音男女「愛國人士」，在ifc手舞足蹈，最後不敵四方八面匯聚的中環友（西裝友、OL、外籍人士等），「五大訴求缺一不可」加港歌，成功蓋過國歌（黨歌），紅色陣營終落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\n──願榮光和戰績歸香港。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n觀音像下智慧之言 (左丁山)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n國際接軌睡午覺 (李純恩)"},{"pid":"39ad6640d2198ecb02e8db507f97d7710a7b4671","tid":1568877,"uid":266683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:05:55.000Z","msg":"Amazon文具助養計劃：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AMAZON0101\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAMAZON0101&d=DHtl%2BAGMG05sKYyicqAXSt%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=4a7d6fe4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AMAZON0101</a><br />\n<br />\n小朋友有需要補充請過黎shopping<br />\n家長亦可提供sponsor🙏🏻"},{"pid":"569ee66a3435ef1c37134ce518a7a1db0dde4e5a","tid":1568877,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">[連儂文宣] 用CHINAZI喚醒藍絲廢老對共賊既不信任！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1567514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1567514</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YhY7uXD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYhY7uXD.jpg&h=5cadd691&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}